---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Home
---
<section class="home">
  <h1>Raoul Paraschiv</h1>
  <p class="tagline">Game designer. Thinking out loud about systems, tools, and craft.</p>

  <div class="home-sections">
    <div>
      <h2><a href="/lab/">Lab</a></h2>
      <p>Projects in progress.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h2><a href="/vault/">Vault</a></h2>
      <p>Completed games and released work.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h2><a href="/commonplace/">Commonplace Book</a></h2>
      <p>Notes on game design, tools, pipelines, and the rest.</p>
      {% if collections.posts.length %}
      <ul class="recent-posts">
        {% for post in collections.posts | reverse | slice(0, 3) %}
          <li><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a> <span>{{ post.date | dateDisplay }}</span></li>
        {% endfor %}
      </ul>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
